OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1776409519
OL,3,CGovernment reportedly drawing up
OL,4,C'worst case scenario' plans for food
OL,5,Cshortages
OL,7,FSeparately, Health Secretary Wes
OL,8,FStreeting told LBC he was "confident"
OL,9,Fthat NHS supplies would remain
OL,10,Fresilient, but added there were plans
OL,11,Fto prioritise ambulances should diesel
OL,12,Fshortages materialise.
OL,14,FHe added: "The likelihood of us
OL,15,Fneeding to activate these worst-case
OL,16,Fscenario plans is reassuringly low."
