OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1776409519
OL,3,CGovernment reportedly drawing up
OL,4,C'worst case scenario' plans for food
OL,5,Cshortages
OL,7,FResponding to the reports, a
OL,8,Fgovernment spokesperson said: "We took
OL,9,Fdecisive action last month to shore up
OL,10,Fthe UK's critical supplies of CO2 by
OL,11,Ftemporarily restarting the Ensus
OL,12,Fbioethanol plant in Teesside and are
OL,13,Fcontinuing to work closely with
OL,14,Fbusiness groups to tackle the impacts
OL,15,Fof events in the Middle East.
OL,17,F"Reasonable worst-case scenarios are a
OL,18,Fplanning tool used by experts and are
OL,19,Fnot a prediction of future events."
OL,26,@{D@cO]
