OL,3,CGovernment reportedly drawing up
OL,4,C'worst case scenario' plans for food
OL,5,Cshortages
OL,7,FITV News understands the Ensus plant
OL,8,Fwill operate for three months to
OL,9,Fincrease domestic CO2 production.
OL,11,FA Downing Street spokesperson
OL,12,Freiterated, "shortages of CO2 are not
OL,13,Fa concern for our economy".
OL,15,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,16,Four political experts are across all
OL,17,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,18,Fto the latest episode below...
